{
  "stem": "7600.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I went upstairs, and I knew right away something happened because everybody sat there crying.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we had heard that Hitler had marched into Austria.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was like a welcoming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Not one of the-- the army, nobody stopped him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Not only-- they threw bouquets at him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "With open arms, he was-- you know, I mean, when they say they-- when later on, they kept on saying they were the first victim.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They weren't victims.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "They were perfectly willing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And life became absolutely horrendous, right away, because you couldn't go on the street.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "They would pick up people on the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Wherever you saw a group of people, they would pick up [INAUDIBLE], mostly-- you know, people-- businessmen, with business suits-- make them scrub the floor, the sidewalk, sometimes with a toothbrush.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They made-- they took Jewish men with the beards [INAUDIBLE], they made them write on the-- on the-- on the shops, don't buy from the Jews.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "Or the Jews are, you know, something terrible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So it was absolutely horrible to go out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "We tried not to go out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And this was in March.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Now, two months later in May-- oh, my mother kept-- my mother had the best idea at that point.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "She said to my father, take all the money we have and go over the border.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "You can go to the-- you know, we all had passports in those days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We had a passport.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So just take the money and go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He could have gone to Belgium.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He could have gone to France.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He could have gone anywhere because there was no such-- just go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he said, are you crazy?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I'm going to leave you and the children here alone?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "What are you going to do?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Says, we have our relatives.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
